cold
and
thin.”
“I
own
I
felt
something
of
what
you
describe,”
said
Mr.
Utterson.
“Quite
so,
sir,”
returned
Poole.
“Well,
when
that
masked
thing
like
a
monkey
jumped
from
among
the
chemicals
and
whipped
into
the
cabinet,
it
went
down
